CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 3, reads: "4. Between duties at the fair, Mrs. Prothro found time for an interview with Kathy Maddox [misprint - should be Cathy Milton] of Radio Station WMCK"
TitMainTitle: Radio broadcaster Cathy Maddox Milton, and Louise Prothro seated in WMCK booth in Syria Mosque for 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, another version
